[u][b]Description:[/b][/u] I will show you some ways on how to keep your code very clean, and give you advice on some programming habits.
[u][b]Difficulty:[/b][/u] Close to 2/10
[u][b]Assumed Knowledge: [/b][/u]Understandment of the basics of Java, at least.

